{"parse":{"title":"Centre for Bhutan Studies and GNH Research","pageid":18008792,"revid":793500081,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>The Centre for Bhutan Studies and GNH Research</b> (formerly The Centre for Bhutan Studies) is a research institute located in <a href=\"/wiki/Thimphu\" title=\"Thimphu\">Thimphu</a>, Bhutan established in 1999 with the purpose of promoting research and scholarship on Bhutan.\n</p><p>The President of the Centre is <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Dasho_Karma_Ura&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dasho Karma Ura (page does not exist)\">Dasho Karma Ura</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Periodical\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Periodical</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Books\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Books</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Centre_for_Bhutan_Studies_and_GNH_Research&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Periodical\">Periodical</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Centre_for_Bhutan_Studies_and_GNH_Research&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Periodical\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Since 1999 the Centre has regularly published an  <a href=\"/wiki/English_language\" title=\"English language\">English language</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Academic_journal\" title=\"Academic journal\">academic journal</a> <b>The Journal of Bhutan Studies</b>. PDF copies of articles published in this journal are freely available online.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Books\">Books</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Centre_for_Bhutan_Studies_and_GNH_Research&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Books\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><cite id=\"CITEREFChodenDeselDorjiKinga2003\" class=\"citation\">Choden, Tashi; Desel, Pema; Dorji, Lham; Kinga, Sonam; Penjore, Dorji (2003), <i>Secret Ballots in Rural Heartland: Gup Elections, 2002</i>, Thimphu: Centre for Bhutan Studies, <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/99936-14-09-7\" title=\"Special:BookSources/99936-14-09-7\">99936-14-09-7</a></cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Secret+Ballots+in+Rural+H